experimental (for example, if the power goes down at my house, the server will power off until I<br/>
reset it, so some readings may be missing) right now, but provides some sense of historical<br/>
information. The data is uploaded whenever modified (typically every 2 hours) to a tex tfile<br/>
located at http://www.butera.org/toccoa/gauge.txt </div>
